Package Tests

Class ControllerTests

java.lang.Object
Tests.ControllerTests
public class ControllerTests extends Object
ControllerTests is a class that tests different scenarios for the parseFile function of the Controller class. A ControllerTests is composed of:
  • A Controller

H4122
